org.eclipse.jst.ws.jaxws.dom.integration.navigator
Interface ILoadingWsProject

public interface ILoadingWsProject

An interface presenting not loaded web service project. This interface is used to be added to the project explorer WS tree in cases when the project is relevant but it is not yet loaded by DOM loader.

Author:
Georgi Vachkov
